  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is a really unique hotel if you're looking for something a bit different on your ski holiday. The building dates back to the 16th century and there's lots of original features to enjoy. We love the stone walls, cosy rooms and log fireplace near the bar. It's less than a mile from Courmayer (there are regular buses) and close to the ski lifts. In fact, you can almost ski back to the door.</p>]]></listingDescription>
