  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people and feature a shower, hairdryer, TV and most have a view of the mountain. A room with a balcony can be requested but not guaranteed. The rooms are simple in style with traditional curtains and bedding, wooden and white painted walls with a minimalist cosy feel. </p>
